                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-74-off401 t17831210-74-cd402"></join> last, one large silver table spoon, value 6 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-74-victim893" type="victimName">
